org.gvsig.export.spi

Interface ExportService

  • All Superinterfaces:
    CancellableTask, MonitorableTask
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractExportService, ExportCSVService, ExportDBFService, ExportDXFService, ExportJDBCService, ExportKMLService, ExportShapeService

    public interface ExportService
extends MonitorableTask

    This service is used to export a source FeatureStore to a target FeatureStore.

    It inherits if MonitorableTask, and it means that the export process can be monitorized by one or more observers that can listen all the export events.
